                    <div class="faq-answer-content">
                        All plans include native integrations with Salesforce and HubSpot. Growth and Enterprise plans include additional integrations with Outreach, Salesloft, Gong, and more. Enterprise customers also get API access for custom integrations.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    How do expert payouts work?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/>
                    </svg>
